go through a breakup after coming here.

109
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,160
And there are stages to it.

110
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:58,080
At first, it gets harder
to get him on the phone.

111
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:00,880
He either ignores your call
or says he'll call back later. Then,

112
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,680
he will sound aloof
and his answers will be very short.

113
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:06,600
And finally, he will drop the bomb.

114
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:09,040
"I'm sorry. I think we should break up."

115
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:11,040
"I'm seeing someone else."

116
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,360
