but this is what her father wants.

242
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,120
We should respect his wish.

243
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:40,240
-Okay, I got it.
-Don't worry. We won't tell.

244
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:46,000
I won't see Bok-ju anyway.

245
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:54,480
Our friendship is over after this year.

246
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,200
I love you, Joon-hyung.

247
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:15,080
Finally. Why is it so difficult
to get a hold of you?

248
00:15:15,640 --> 00:15:18,240
