semi-professional teams.

795
00:50:48,160 --> 00:50:49,200
Yes.

796
00:50:50,280 --> 00:50:53,680
Some of you are embarking
on completely new paths.

797
00:50:54,280 --> 00:50:55,400
Anyhow,

798
00:50:57,800 --> 00:50:59,200
let's not forget about...

799
00:51:00,280 --> 00:51:01,800
our times together.

800
00:51:10,680 --> 00:51:12,080
Call me whenever you're stressed out.

801
00:51:14,880 --> 00:51:16,200
Coach Choi and I...

802
00:51:17,280 --> 00:51:18,600
will always be here for you.

803
00:51:21,440 --> 00:51:23,120
-Thank you, Head Coach.
-Thank you, Head Coach.

804
00:51:23,760 --> 00:51:25,040
Congratulations on your graduation.

805
00:51:25,280 --> 00:51:26,600
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

806
00:51:45,800 --> 00:51:47,200
Weightlifter Yoon Jin-hee

807
00:51:48,160 --> 00:51:49,240
Bok-ju.

808
00:51:50,760 --> 00:51:52,800
Hey, Ye-bin.

809
00:51:53,120 --> 00:51:55,480
Thanks for putting up with us
all these years.

810
00:51:55,600 --> 00:51:57,440
Just thanking us isn't enough.

811
00:51:58,280 --> 00:51:59,880
Don't think we'll go easy on you.

812
00:52:00,040 --> 00:52:02,760
You must do what you have
to do before you leave.

813
00:52:03,160 --> 00:52:05,760
All right. Time for
the highlight of the graduation day!

814
00:52:06,200 --> 00:52:08,880
The weightlifting team's fashion show
begins now!

815
00:52:12,160 --> 00:52:13,760
-Go, Nan-hee!
-Nice!

816
00:52:17,080 --> 00:52:18,280
Bravo!

817
00:52:30,280 --> 00:52:33,600
Please give it up for our
weightlifting fairy, Kim Bok-ju!

818
00:52:39,280 --> 00:52:40,840
Go, Bok-ju.

819
00:52:40,920 --> 00:52:42,520
-You're so awesome!
-Kim Bok-ju!

820
00:52:51,880 --> 00:52:54,480
-Bok-ju!
-Hey, go stand in front of it.

821
00:52:54,560 --> 00:52:56,120
Hey, why are you...

822
00:52:58,800 --> 00:53:00,920
Gosh, you guys can't take anything pink.

823
00:53:01,520 --> 00:53:03,560
-Snatch it.
-I got it!

824
00:53:03,680 --> 00:53:05,080
Let go!

825
00:53:08,560 --> 00:53:10,080
Her shoes. Grab her shoes.

826
00:53:10,160 --> 00:53:11,640
-No!
-We got it!

827
00:53:12,680 --> 00:53:14,840
No. Who took my socks?

828
00:53:15,720 --> 00:53:17,800
-Hey, grab her!
-Come here!

829
00:53:18,280 --> 00:53:19,680
Hey, get her.

830
00:53:24,440 --> 00:53:26,880
-Snatch it.
-Gosh!

831
00:53:26,960 --> 00:53:28,440
I got her shoe!

832
00:53:30,680 --> 00:53:32,280
-Hey!
-Get back here!

833
00:53:32,680 --> 00:53:34,120
Danger! Keep Out

834
00:53:35,880 --> 00:53:36,960
-Guys!
-Joon-hyung.

835
00:53:37,040 --> 00:53:38,880
-Joon-hyung.
-Joon-hyung, come on.

836
00:53:38,960 --> 00:53:39,960
Guys, take his clothes off.

837
00:53:40,040 --> 00:53:42,360
-Take it.
-I thought you guys were going out.

838
00:53:42,800 --> 00:53:44,960
-Lift him.
-Wait! I'll give you guys money.

839
00:53:47,280 --> 00:53:49,120
The graduation ceremony
will begin shortly.

840
00:53:49,280 --> 00:53:50,600
Let's get this over with, okay?

841
00:53:50,880 --> 00:53:52,880
-Let's go.
-Let's go!

842
00:53:55,000 --> 00:53:56,160
Salute!

843
00:53:56,280 --> 00:54:00,080
Sergeant Cho Tae-kwon is here
to attend the graduation ceremony!

844
00:54:00,200 --> 00:54:02,800
-Just in time.
-Help me, Tae-kwon!

845
00:54:02,880 --> 00:54:05,280
You wish. Let's do this, guys!

846
00:54:06,160 --> 00:54:07,520
No, no. Guys, please.

847
00:54:07,600 --> 00:54:09,320
No. No! Gosh!

848
00:54:09,400 --> 00:54:11,600
-In one, two, three.
-In one, two, three.

849
00:54:25,120 --> 00:54:26,200
Bok-ju!

850
00:54:26,840 --> 00:54:28,680
Oh, hello!

851
00:54:28,760 --> 00:54:29,960
-Hello.
-Hi.

852
00:54:31,680 --> 00:54:33,880
This is Bok-ju's dad,
and this is her uncle.

853
00:54:34,480 --> 00:54:35,880
-Hello.
-Hello.

854
00:54:36,160 --> 00:54:37,720
These are Joon-hyung's parents.

855
00:54:37,800 --> 00:54:40,280
This is his brother,
and she's his fiancÃ©e.

856
00:54:41,000 --> 00:54:43,280
It's a pleasure to finally meet you.
I'm Kim Chang-geol.

857
00:54:43,640 --> 00:54:47,160
Thank you for those vitamins
you sent me. They're great.

858
00:54:47,240 --> 00:54:50,800
It's nothing compared to all
the fried chicken you've sent us.

859
00:54:50,880 --> 00:54:52,600
They're so delicious.

860
00:54:53,240 --> 00:54:54,680
You're a master of fried chicken.

861
00:54:56,400 --> 00:54:59,360
To be honest, I deep-fry
70 percent of our fried chicken.

862
00:54:59,640 --> 00:55:02,240
Please visit our restaurant.
I'll close it for the day...

863
00:55:03,000 --> 00:55:05,120
and make as much
fried chicken as you want.

864
00:55:05,720 --> 00:55:08,440
Then we'll give you
red ginseng drink in return.

865
00:55:08,720 --> 00:55:10,160
Please visit our pharmacy.

866
00:55:11,160 --> 00:55:13,160
It looks as if you two
are getting engaged.

867
00:55:13,640 --> 00:55:14,640
Congratulations.

868
00:55:14,880 --> 00:55:16,200
You got me a gift, right?

869
00:55:17,560 --> 00:55:18,640
Congratulations, Bok-ju.

870
00:55:18,720 --> 00:55:20,800
Congratulations on
setting your wedding date.

871
00:55:20,880 --> 00:55:23,200
-Congratulations, Dr Go.
-Thanks.

872
00:55:23,520 --> 00:55:25,920
You'll need to help me out
when we become sisters-in-law.

873
00:55:26,080 --> 00:55:27,480
You know how clumsy I am, right?

874
00:55:27,880 --> 00:55:29,080
Gosh, stop it.

875
00:55:31,240 --> 00:55:32,400
Here, Bok-ju.

876
00:55:32,480 --> 00:55:33,880
-Thank you.
-Joon-hyung, here.

877
00:55:35,000 --> 00:55:36,240
Dad, smell these flowers.

878
00:55:36,320 --> 00:55:38,280
-Bok-ju.
-Bok-ju, let's take photos.

879
00:55:38,360 --> 00:55:39,600
Hello, everyone.

880
00:55:39,680 --> 00:55:43,040
I, Sergeant Cho Tae-kwon,
will be your photographer today.

881
00:55:43,120 --> 00:55:44,160
Hello, hello.

882
00:55:44,240 --> 00:55:46,880
Shall we start with Joon-hyung's family?

883
00:55:46,960 --> 00:55:49,080
All right. Please stand right there.
I'll take a few photos.

884
00:55:49,280 --> 00:55:52,080
In one, two, three.

885
00:56:05,960 --> 00:56:08,160
I guess I won't be able
to come here after today.

886
00:56:09,080 --> 00:56:12,480
I can probably buy 100 chickens
with all the change I threw here.

887
00:56:13,160 --> 00:56:15,560
Thanks to it,
you achieved all of your dreams.

888
00:56:15,800 --> 00:56:18,400
You joined the national team
and even got a boyfriend.

889
00:56:19,240 --> 00:56:20,360
A handsome boyfriend.

890
00:56:21,360 --> 00:56:22,480
What are you saying?

891
00:56:23,240 --> 00:56:24,280
You don't think I'm handsome?

892
00:56:25,280 --> 00:56:27,880
Fine. I'll give it to you as
your graduation gift. You're handsome.

893
00:56:33,160 --> 00:56:36,360
So many things happened on this campus
in the last four years.

894
00:56:37,480 --> 00:56:39,880
I trained hard...

895
00:56:40,080 --> 00:56:43,280
and ate a lot with Nan-hee and Seon-ok.

896
00:56:43,840 --> 00:56:45,760
We spent so much time together, too.

897
00:56:53,600 --> 00:56:55,800
I think I'll miss this place a lot, too.

898
00:56:56,040 --> 00:57:00,440
I ran so hard here
and even had to drag tires around it.

899
00:57:01,880 --> 00:57:03,720
When do you have to go back
to Taereung tomorrow?

900
00:57:03,800 --> 00:57:06,280
-Do you think you'll get on the match?
-I think so.

901
00:57:06,480 --> 00:57:09,880
One of the senior members has a
shoulder injury, so I'll probably...

902
00:57:10,160 --> 00:57:12,720
Listen to you. That's awesome!

903
00:57:12,800 --> 00:57:15,360
Do you want to bet on who will win
more medals at the Tokyo Olympics?

904
00:57:15,440 --> 00:57:18,200
-How about 100 dollars? Are you in?
-Hey, 100 dollars is too little.

905
00:57:18,360 --> 00:57:19,880
It should be 1,000 dollars at least.

906
00:57:20,080 --> 00:57:23,760
Besides, I'll be more famous than you
after the Olympics.

907
00:57:23,840 --> 00:57:25,280
Do you want my autograph?

908
00:57:25,440 --> 00:57:28,440
My gosh. Just make sure I'll be able
to see you in Japan.

909
00:57:30,760 --> 00:57:31,840
Bok-ju.

910
00:57:34,400 --> 00:57:36,240
If I win a gold medal this time,

911
00:57:38,480 --> 00:57:39,680
will you marry me?

912
00:57:41,400 --> 00:57:42,720
I'll get pension.

913
00:57:43,160 --> 00:57:44,600
I'll take care of you.

914
00:57:45,400 --> 00:57:46,680
I'll think about it.

915
00:57:47,720 --> 00:57:50,720
