if you want to win a gold medal?

916
00:57:51,200 --> 00:57:52,600
With that said, let's run together.

917
00:57:53,720 --> 00:57:56,640
Why would you want to run
on our graduation day? No way.

918
00:57:56,760 --> 00:57:58,360
You big slacker.

919
00:57:58,440 --> 00:58:00,880
Your body will stiffen
if you slack off even just a day.

920
00:58:00,960 --> 00:58:02,880
-Let's run.
-No.

921
00:58:02,960 --> 00:58:05,080
-Let's run.
-I said no.

922
00:58:06,800 --> 00:58:08,000
I won't marry you.

923
00:58:09,120 --> 00:58:11,200
Hey. What do you mean you won't marry me?

924
00:58:11,280 --> 00:58:13,880
If you say that,
now I have no choice but to run.

925
00:58:15,280 --> 00:58:16,480
I won't marry you.

926
00:58:17,240 --> 00:58:18,240
Hurry up.

927
00:58:19,280 --> 00:58:20,280
Hug me.

928
00:58:20,720 --> 00:58:22,840
Everyone has their youthful years.

929
00:58:23,880 --> 00:58:26,040
It's a brightly sparkling time...

930
00:58:26,800 --> 00:58:29,600
made more beautiful
because of our immaturity.

931
00:58:31,160 --> 00:58:33,640
We're not afraid because
we have nothing to lose,

932
00:58:34,280 --> 00:58:37,200
and our hearts flutter because
we have endless possibilities.

933
00:58:39,200 --> 00:58:40,720
As a 24-year-old youth,

934
00:58:41,440 --> 00:58:43,640
I'm not complete yet,

935
00:58:44,360 --> 00:58:46,840
but I'm already more than perfect.

936
00:59:38,640 --> 00:59:40,680
Weightlifting Fairy
